original: Linder, Estrid Kristina, läroverksadjunkt, Karlskrona, f. i Ljusne, Gäv-leb. 1., av Lars L. o. Pauline Lindqvist. — Stud :ex. i Upps. 15, fil. mag. där 23 o. provår 29. E. o. ämneslär. i Säffle 24-25, vik. adj. i Boden 30-32, e. o. lektor i Söderhamn 32-36, adj. i tyska o. eng. v. Karlskr. h. a. 1. sed. 37. Stud:res. t. Tyskl. o. Engl.
translated: Linder, Estrid Kristina, teacher, Karlskrona, born in Ljusne, Gävleborg County, 1st of Lars L. and Pauline Lindqvist. — Studied at Uppsala University, obtained a bachelor's degree in 1915, a Master's degree in 1923, and completed a probationary year in 1929. Temporary subject teacher in Säffle from 1924-1925, substitute teacher in Boden from 1930-1932, acting lecturer in Söderhamn from 1932-1936, and teacher of German and English in Karlskrona from 1937 until the present. Studied abroad in Germany and England.
